[
  {
    "text": "George Karas: Hello, my name is George Karas, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=0"
  },
  {
    "text": "and I am part of Apple's Video Partner Operations team.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=2"
  },
  {
    "text": "Welcome to this video to understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=5"
  },
  {
    "text": "the video integration with the Apple TV app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=7"
  },
  {
    "text": "For TV providers that are integrating ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=9"
  },
  {
    "text": "their own video application with the Apple TV app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=11"
  },
  {
    "text": "this video will detail the client requirements ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=13"
  },
  {
    "text": "and onboarding process that are necessary to adhere to.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=15"
  },
  {
    "text": "Let's start with understanding ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=18"
  },
  {
    "text": "how your video apps will integrate.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=19"
  },
  {
    "text": "There are three basic things that will need to be achieved.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=22"
  },
  {
    "text": "First, your iOS and tvOS applications ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=25"
  },
  {
    "text": "will need to include the universal search extended entitlement ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=28"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your provisioning profile, so that they can share ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=30"
  },
  {
    "text": "the authentication status of the customer to the device.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=33"
  },
  {
    "text": "While customers watch content in your application, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=36"
  },
  {
    "text": "playback data is reported to the device as well, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=38"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that it can be tracked in the Up Next section ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=41"
  },
  {
    "text": "of the Apple TV app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=43"
  },
  {
    "text": "And your application has to support deep-linking ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=45"
  },
  {
    "text": "to properly open content for browsing, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=47"
  },
  {
    "text": "play content automatically, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=49"
  },
  {
    "text": "and resume VOD content correctly.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=51"
  },
  {
    "text": "Registering subscriptions correctly is critical to ensure ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=54"
  },
  {
    "text": "your applications work correctly with the data you are providing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=57"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your catalog and availability feeds, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=59"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is controlling the presentation of your content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=62"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the Apple TV app for our customers.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=64"
  },
  {
    "text": "As customers are authenticated to your application, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=66"
  },
  {
    "text": "this status is shared with the device ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=69"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that the Apple TV app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=70"
  },
  {
    "text": "can properly understand your entitlement data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=72"
  },
  {
    "text": "and show content as playable ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=74"
  },
  {
    "text": "or available as part of a subscription package.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=75"
  },
  {
    "text": "As customers change their subscription status, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=78"
  },
  {
    "text": "the registration with the Apple TV app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=81"
  },
  {
    "text": "must also be udpated.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=82"
  },
  {
    "text": "And the customer's subscription status and expiration date ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=84"
  },
  {
    "text": "should also be properly adjusted as your application is launched.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=87"
  },
  {
    "text": "If you are using restriction tiers ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=91"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your availability feeds for the Apple TV app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=92"
  },
  {
    "text": "then tiered entitlements must also be presented ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=95"
  },
  {
    "text": "in the subscription registration.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=97"
  },
  {
    "text": "These tier names must match your availability feeds, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=99"
  },
  {
    "text": "and it's important that they represent ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=102"
  },
  {
    "text": "consumer-facing packages of content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=104"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ensure your applications perform with a minimum payload ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=106"
  },
  {
    "text": "against the Apple TV app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=108"
  },
  {
    "text": "To support tracking content in Up Next of the Apple TV app, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=110"
  },
  {
    "text": "your applications must report video playback information.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=113"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is done through the Now Playing API, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=117"
  },
  {
    "text": "which includes the contentId value ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=119"
  },
  {
    "text": "used in the catalog feed for VOD movies and TV shows, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=121"
  },
  {
    "text": "or the serviceId value used in the linear availability feed ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=123"
  },
  {
    "text": "for the channel that is being played.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=126"
  },
  {
    "text": "Video on demand content ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=128"
  },
  {
    "text": "also requires the duration of the video asset ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=130"
  },
  {
    "text": "and the elapsed time of the customer to be shared ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=132"
  },
  {
    "text": "to understand if a customer has completed watching a video asset ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=134"
  },
  {
    "text": "or if it has time remaining ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=136"
  },
  {
    "text": "and can be resumed later from Up Next.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=138"
  },
  {
    "text": "This data is updated on activity events ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=140"
  },
  {
    "text": "as customers interact with your video player ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=142"
  },
  {
    "text": "such as play, pause, seek ahead or behind, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=144"
  },
  {
    "text": "and upon any exit of the video player.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=148"
  },
  {
    "text": "The Apple TV app also needs to understand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=151"
  },
  {
    "text": "the content a customer is browsing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=153"
  },
  {
    "text": "for it to enable a nice Siri feature.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=154"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is done through the NSUserActivity API, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=157"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is present while a customer is viewing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=160"
  },
  {
    "text": "a content details page for a movie or TV show ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=162"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your application.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=164"
  },
  {
    "text": "Again, the contentId values for your content from the feeds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=166"
  },
  {
    "text": "are used here, so that a customer can say, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=168"
  },
  {
    "text": "\"Hey Siri, add this to my Up Next.\" ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=171"
  },
  {
    "text": "Great for those save-for-later moments.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=173"
  },
  {
    "text": "And finally, proper deep-linking is critical ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=176"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ensure your customers have a pleasant experience ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=179"
  },
  {
    "text": "from the Apple TV app to your own app.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=181"
  },
  {
    "text": "Your applications must accept open links ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=183"
  },
  {
    "text": "for all of the content types you are providing ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=185"
  },
  {
    "text": "in your metadata feeds.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=187"
  },
  {
    "text": "Accepting play links properly is a requirement ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=189"
  },
  {
    "text": "for movie, TV episode, and sporting event items, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=191"
  },
  {
    "text": "and are presented and used by the Apple TV app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=194"
  },
  {
    "text": "when the customer is recognized as entitled ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=196"
  },
  {
    "text": "via the subscription registration ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=198"
  },
  {
    "text": "mentioned previously.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=200"
  },
  {
    "text": "Lastly, for your VOD movies and TV shows, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=202"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple will add a resumeTime parameter ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=205"
  },
  {
    "text": "to your play deep-links with the time value in seconds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=207"
  },
  {
    "text": "if the Apple TV app recognizes the customer has time remaining ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=209"
  },
  {
    "text": "to finish watching.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=212"
  },
  {
    "text": "The expectation is then that your video player ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=214"
  },
  {
    "text": "will resume at the appropriate time.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=216"
  },
  {
    "text": "Deep-links from the Apple TV app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=219"
  },
  {
    "text": "must also meet the Human Interface Guidelines ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=220"
  },
  {
    "text": "to ensure the experience is elegant for the customer.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=222"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once your applications include these integrations, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=226"
  },
  {
    "text": "they're ready for testing by Apple.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=228"
  },
  {
    "text": "As your development tracks have begun ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=230"
  },
  {
    "text": "across the metadata feeds and app integration, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=232"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple will support you through the onboarding process.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=234"
  },
  {
    "text": "Part of this is sharing the necessary data ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=237"
  },
  {
    "text": "about your services and brand, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=239"
  },
  {
    "text": "which is done through the partner manifest.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=241"
  },
  {
    "text": "This is a collection of your catalog ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=243"
  },
  {
    "text": "and availability services, and is shared with Apple ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=245"
  },
  {
    "text": "so that they can be set up in our systems.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=248"
  },
  {
    "text": "The manifest is a living feed of your services, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=250"
  },
  {
    "text": "allowing you to manage them in Apple's systems as well, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=253"
  },
  {
    "text": "should the feed URLs change, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=255"
  },
  {
    "text": "or you later work with Apple to graduate to a new spec version.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=256"
  },
  {
    "text": "Coming onboard to the Apple TV app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=261"
  },
  {
    "text": "generally works in the following fashion.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=262"
  },
  {
    "text": "When selected to participate in the program, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=264"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple will engage with your technical development teams ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=266"
  },
  {
    "text": "in an official kickoff meeting ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=269"
  },
  {
    "text": "and possibly set up some workshops to follow later.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=270"
  },
  {
    "text": "Through the partner manifest, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=273"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple can set up your video service brand ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=274"
  },
  {
    "text": "and register your video applications in our systems.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=277"
  },
  {
    "text": "This then allows Apple to begin receiving your feeds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=280"
  },
  {
    "text": "once that development and validation exercise ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=282"
  },
  {
    "text": "with the Media Feed Validator has begun.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=284"
  },
  {
    "text": "It's often recommended to start on this work stream first, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=287"
  },
  {
    "text": "as application testing requires it, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=290"
  },
  {
    "text": "and Apple can require up to a two-week cycle ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=292"
  },
  {
    "text": "to validate and test an ingestion of your feeds.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=294"
  },
  {
    "text": "App development can begin in parallel, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=297"
  },
  {
    "text": "but certain points of information are required ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=299"
  },
  {
    "text": "on the catalog and availability feeds ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=301"
  },
  {
    "text": "being generated for full validation ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=303"
  },
  {
    "text": "and, of course, testing.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=305"
  },
  {
    "text": "Once the metadata feeds are fully approved by Apple, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=307"
  },
  {
    "text": "and applications with the integrations ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=309"
  },
  {
    "text": "described in this video are included ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=311"
  },
  {
    "text": "and shared with Apple via TestFlight, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=313"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple TV app test mode can begin.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=315"
  },
  {
    "text": "At this point, you can simply ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=317"
  },
  {
    "text": "install your application from TestFlight, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=318"
  },
  {
    "text": "and experience it a part of the Apple TV app ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=320"
  },
  {
    "text": "as if it's publicly available.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=322"
  },
  {
    "text": "Apple does the same, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=325"
  },
  {
    "text": "and runs the application through a formal QA testing process ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=326"
  },
  {
    "text": "before the builds are submitted to the App Store for review.",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=329"
  },
  {
    "text": "Upon Apple QA approval, the applications ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=333"
  },
  {
    "text": "can be submitted to the App Store for review, ",
    "link": "https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/tech-talks-509/?time=335"
  },
  {
    "text": "and once live on the App Store, ",
